	.string "{PLAYER}: Hi! Thanks a lot for the\n"
	.string "rail PASS!\p"
	.string "{PLAYER}: Pardon?\p"
	.string "{PLAYER}: Is it that fun to mimic\n"
	.string "my every move?$"

